+        (t2 - t0)/(t1 - t0) = (g2 - g0)/(g1 - g0), so
+        (t2 - t0) = (t1 - t0) * (g2 - g0)/(g1 - g0), so
+        t2 = t0 + (t1 - t0) * (g2 - g0)/(g1 - g0), where
+        t2 is the logical stop time of the output.
